## Description {#details}

A post-order depth-first <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/lazycallgraph/refscc">RefSCC</a> iterator over the call graph.

This iterator walks the cached post-order sequence of RefSCCs. However, it trades stability for flexibility. It is restricted to a forward iterator but will survive mutations which insert new RefSCCs and continue to point to the same <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/lazycallgraph/refscc">RefSCC</a> even if it moves in the post-order sequence.
